snippet.title: Neko Para Vol.1 Opening Theme Song (HD)
snippet.description:
"Taiyou Paradise" Opening theme song from 'Neko Para Vol.1' a lovely visual novel develop by NEKO WORKs. 
Available now on steam. 

Song Title: Taiyou Paradise (タイヨウパラダイス)
Lyrics: 雪仁
Arrangement: 水城新人
Song: nao

Watch "Doki Doki kokoro" Opening song from 'Neko Para Vol.2' here https://youtu.be/e0WCIEvfaLA
